org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.commons.utils

Class Asserts

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.commons.utils.Asserts

  • public class Asserts
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains typically usually used asserts. The asserts check a condition an throws a AssertionError if the condition does not satisfy the assertion.
